### AI Workflows API — 包含版本快照 (versions / diff / rollback)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!

### 登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 查询工作流列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workflows?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 创建工作流
# @name createWorkflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workflows
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试版本快照工作流",
  "description": "用于验证版本快照功能",
  "canvasJson": "{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":\"start\",\"type\":\"default\",\"position\":{\"x\":100,\"y\":100},\"data\":{\"label\":\"开始\"}}],\"edges\":[]}",
  "definitionJson": "{}"
}

###
@workflowId = {{createWorkflow.response.body.$.data.id}}

### 查询工作流详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workflows/{{workflowId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 校验工作流
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workflows/{{workflowId}}/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 发布工作流（自动写版本快照 v1）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workflows/{{workflowId}}/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 修改画布后再次发布（写版本快照 v2）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workflows/{{workflowId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "canvasJson": "{\"nodes\":[{\"id\":\"start\",\"type\":\"default\",\"position\":{\"x\":100,\"y\":100},\"data\":{\"label\":\"开始\"}},{\"id\":\"llm1\",\"type\":\"llm\",\"position\":{\"x\":300,\"y\":100},\"data\":{\"label\":\"LLM节点\"}}],\"edges\":[{\"id\":\"e1\",\"source\":\"start\",\"target\":\"llm1\"}]}",
  "definitionJson": "{}"
}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workflows/{{workflowId}}/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ── 版本历史 ──

### 查询版本历史列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workflows/{{workflowId}}/versions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 查询版本差异（v1 → v2）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workflows/{{workflowId}}/versions/diff?from=1&to=2
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 版本回滚（回滚到 v1，创建新版本 v3）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workflows/{{workflowId}}/versions/1/rollback
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 回滚后查看版本列表（应看到 v1/v2/v3）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workflows/{{workflowId}}/versions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 查询版本差异（回滚前后 v2 → v3 应与 v1 内容相近）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workflows/{{workflowId}}/versions/diff?from=2&to=3
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 查询工作流节点类型
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai-workflows/node-types
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
